SubjectRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain Regulations Made Under the Canada National Parks Act
PrecisRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE CANADA NATIONAL PARKS ACT, to amend the relevant provisions of the national park regulations that are currently applicable to the Town of Jasper to allow the Town to implement its bylaws to achieve self-governance.
